        <abstract>
            <p>CD’s plans are uncertain because of his daughter’s [Henrietta Darwin] fever.</p>
            <p>If GR would kindly reserve rooms for CD near college, CD will write before the meeting [of British Association at Oxford] if he is prevented from coming.</p>
        </abstract>
